A special thank-you goes to Omega Fallon created the Enochian icon, I made that glowing image by the way, so I suppose it's compliant.

Stay tuned for more on this end. If you're looking for info on Enochian, it's been used in a few joke articles and one SCP on the French branch. To paraphrase SCP-340-FR, 

